.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-EXPERIMENT\-TAG" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.2.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-experiment\-tag \- Add or remove short labels on a tracked run
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose experiment tag [OPTIONS] [TAG]...
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Attach short labels ("baseline", "lr\-bug") to a tracked job record. Tags are a sorted set: adding an existing tag or removing an absent one is a no\-op. Defaults to the latest tracked run when no \-\-job\-id is given. Contacts no scheduler; only the tracked record (and its latest\-pointer duplicate, when it names this job) is rewritten.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fITAG\fR
Tags to add; may be omitted when only removing.
.TP
\fB--remove\fR \fITAG\fR
Tag to remove; repeat for multiple tags.
.TP
\fB--job\-id\fR \fIJOB_ID\fR
Tracked Slurm job id to tag; defaults to the latest tracked run.
.TP
\fB-f\fR, \fB--file\fR \fIFILE\fR
Compose specification file to read; if omitted, use the active context compose file or fall back to compose.yaml.
.TP
\fB--format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Possible values: text, json.
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB-v\fR, \fB--verbose\fR
Increase diagnostic verbosity; repeat for debug\-level logs.
.TP
\fB--debug\fR
Enable debug\-level diagnostics (equivalent to \-vv unless RUST_LOG is set).
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--offline\fR
Forbid SSH, remote delegation, Slurm scheduler contact, submissions, allocations, and cancels.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose experiment tag baseline
hpc\-compose experiment tag baseline lr\-bug \-\-job\-id 12345
hpc\-compose experiment tag \-\-remove lr\-bug \-\-job\-id 12345 \-\-format json
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
hpc\-compose(1), hpc\-compose\-experiment(1), hpc\-compose\-experiment\-bundle(1), hpc\-compose\-experiment\-note(1), hpc\-compose\-experiment\-show(1)
